<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Archive wall, column 5, third course. The left side, covering one and a half blocks, is complete except for the upper right corner of the second block, but on the right side one block is broken and partly lost and the right end is wholly lost ; fragments of the lost areas have been found fallen in front of the wall.</p>
</div>
